# Keep test files out of the Vercel deployment bundle.
#
# Vercel turns every top-level file in api/ into a serverless function. A test
# file like api/payments.test.js would therefore be deployed as a function,
# consuming a slot against the Hobby-plan limit of 12 (we are already at 12) and
# potentially failing the build. Excluding them here means they are never
# uploaded, so they can never be mistaken for functions. Vitest reads them from
# the local working tree, so local + CI test runs are unaffected.
*.test.js
*.test.ts
*.test.jsx
*.test.tsx
*.spec.js
*.spec.ts
